
                              Vision Document
                           =====================


1. High level project goals/use cases
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = 

The system will simulate the life of a town. It will simulate the People living
in the town and the Services they interact with in everyday life. The core
services will be: 

  - People Id Registry
  - Hospital
  - Bank
  - People's Life Course Simulation

The system will simulate the time passing by.
  

2. High level architecture
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = 

Service oriented architecture. The components must be organized into independent
modules. It is foreseen that the client access is multi-protocol. Also the
service will be able to exchange message in a client-server mode.


